data.title: Fullsteam Records
data.text: Awarded six times as the "independent label of the year" in Finland, Fullsteam Records is one of the most important sources of exciting new and fresh music from Finland. Fullsteam Records catalogue includes nearly 200 releases from artists like Disco Ensemble, Ismo Alanko, Damn Seagulls, Jaakko & Jay, Callisto, Lapko, Medeia, No Shame, Rubik, Ceebrolistics and Eurocrack.
